develop a multithreaded application where one thread is reading 1 line at once from a file.
another thread calculates the length of the string and converts it into uppercase and prints on the console.
This operation to be done line by line
e.g.
file1.txt
String1
String2 new
String3 added new string
thread1 will read : String1
thread2 will calculate length & convert String1 to STRING1 and print on the console.